= Supported Browsers =

[[SahrisWiki]] supports and is tested on the following web browsers:
* [[http://www.firefox.org|Mozilla Firefox]]
* [[http://www.opera.com/|Opera]]
* [[http://www.apple.com/safari/|Safari]]
* [[http://www.google.com/chrome|Google Chrome]]

[[SahrsWiki]] **does not** support:
* [[http://www.microsoft.com/windows/internet-explorer/|Internet Explorer]]

Why does [[SahrisWiki]] not support Microsoft Internet Explorer ? Simple:
* [[http://www.w3.org/MarkUp/2004/xhtml-faq#ie|Internet Explorer does not support application/xhtml+xml]]
* [[http://whyiesucks.blogspot.com/|Internet Explorer _sucks_]]

